title: Ep91: Legendary Heauxs Feat Mack Wilds & Mouse Jones
itunes:title: Ep91: Legendary Heauxs Feat Mack Wilds & Mouse Jones
description:
This week the duo are back in the studio together and they are joined by Mack Wilds and Mouse Jones. The two start off with a much needed catch up and before they are joined by the new hosts of "Guys Next Door" podcast. The group delve in to a kink we may all be familiar with and then get into much heated discussions along the way. The conversation leads to legendary heauxs and what makes a hoe legendary anyway. Could you cuff/wife a hoe? Then, picking up where they left off from last time, Mouse and Mack Wilds help dissect the need for a "title" from women. Follow the guests on social media @mackwilds @mouse_jones Don't forget to use the hashtag #whoreibledecisions on twitter and follow the hosts on IG @fullcourtpumps @weezywtf @Whoreible_decisions
